Yes, he does, answered Peter. When Jesus entered the house, he spoke first. "What do you think, Simon?" he asked. "Who collects taxes from the kings of the earth? Do they collect them from their sons or from others?"
"From others," Peter answered. "Then the children do not have to pay," Jesus said to him.
